Revision history for Perl extension cyrillic.

2.09  16 Aug 2001
    - added functions cset_factory and case_factory
    - extended detect function for detecting charsets list
    - added koi8-r.map for Unicode::Map

2.08  04 Jul 2001
    - optimized via decreasing of eval blocks

2.06  18 Jun 2001
    - bugfix version
    - modified so it may be used w/ perl 5.005_02

2.02  15 Jun 2001
    - added helper function: charset.
    - chaged return value of detect.
    - detect speed optimized
    - insignificant misprint fixed
    - fixed psevdographic chars converting bug
    - added Unicode and UTF-8 converting
    - added oncall named convertors creation

1.12  04 Jun 2001
    - added functions: lofirst, upfirst.
